name: AbstractScape Vol.1 [Redux]
description:
Cramped studio
apartments of a city. Within every
space, a different story- from the lazy
reflections of those watching
passerbys, to the colorful vibrancy of
those with hyperactive expression
and ambition. The priorities of basic
survival have shifted from food, water,
and shelter, to income, purpose, and
belonging. Like a small cube crushing
everyone to their core, mankind's
inner thoughts are more vibrant than
ever as the new world struggles to
keep pace with how fast it changes,
how much it's grown.
